---
// Resume download is a placeholder until public/resume.pdf is added.
---

<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="hero-tag mono"><span class="dot"></span> ML HARNESS · AGENTIC WORKFLOW · DATA ANALYSIS</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">데이터로 문제를 정의하고,<br>모델로 <em>해결 가능성</em>을 검증하는 분석가</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">ML 프로젝트를 재사용 가능한 하니스로 설계·운영합니다. 정형·비정형 데이터를 모델링부터 배포까지 책임지고, 재현 가능한 실험 구조와 에이전트 역할 분리로 품질을 지킵니다.</p>

      <div class="id-tags">
        <span class="id-tag mono"><span class="marker">●</span> Data Analysis</span>
        <span class="id-tag mono"><span class="marker">●</span> MLOps</span>
        <span class="id-tag mono"><span class="marker">●</span> Agentic Workflow</span>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">프로젝트 보기 →</a>
        <a href="/resume.pdf" class="btn btn-ghost">이력서 다운로드</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/buzziru" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-text">GitHub 보기 ↗</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero visual: animated data pipeline -->
    <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hero-visual-head">
        <span>notebook · pipeline_draft.ipynb</span>
        <div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      </div>

      <svg class="pipeline-svg" viewBox="0 0 420 260" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <marker id="arr" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto">
            <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.25)"></path>
          </marker>
        </defs>

        <!-- nodes -->
        <g font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="10" fill="#b4bcd0">
          <!-- raw data -->
          <rect x="14" y="20" width="86" height="48" rx="4" fill="#1a1a28" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.12)" stroke-width="1"></rect>
          <text x="57" y="40" text-anchor="middle">RAW DATA</text>
          <text x="57" y="56" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6a6b6c" font-size="9">csv · db · api</text>

          <!-- EDA -->
          <rect x="130" y="20" width="86" height="48" rx="4" fill="#1a1a28" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.12)" stroke-width="1"></rect>
          <text x="173" y="40" text-anchor="middle">EDA</text>
          <text x="173" y="56" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6a6b6c" font-size="9">explore · clean</text>

          <!-- Features -->
          <rect x="246" y="20" width="86" height="48" rx="4" fill="#1a1a28" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.12)" stroke-width="1"></rect>
          <text x="289" y="40" text-anchor="middle">FEATURES</text>
          <text x="289" y="56" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6a6b6c" font-size="9">encode · scale</text>

          <!-- Model (accent) -->
          <rect x="130" y="110" width="86" height="48" rx="4" fill="#5e6ad2" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)" stroke-width="1"></rect>
          <text x="173" y="130" text-anchor="middle" fill="#ffffff">MODEL</text>
          <text x="173" y="146" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.6)" font-size="9">sklearn · torch</text>

          <!-- Eval -->
          <rect x="14" y="110" width="86" height="48" rx="4" fill="#1a1a28" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.12)" stroke-width="1"></rect>
          <text x="57" y="130" text-anchor="middle">EVALUATE</text>
          <text x="57" y="146" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6a6b6c" font-size="9">metric · cv</text>

          <!-- Interpret -->
          <rect x="246" y="110" width="86" height="48" rx="4" fill="#1a1a28" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.12)" stroke-width="1"></rect>
          <text x="289" y="130" text-anchor="middle">INTERPRET</text>
          <text x="289" y="146" text-anchor="middle" fill="#6a6b6c" font-size="9">shap · err</text>

          <!-- Report -->
          <rect x="130" y="200" width="86" height="44" rx="4" fill="rgba(94,106,210,0.15)" stroke="rgba(94,106,210,0.4)" stroke-width="1"></rect>
          <text x="173" y="222" text-anchor="middle" fill="#ba9cff">REPORT</text>
          <text x="173" y="236" text-anchor="middle" fill="#7877c6" font-size="9">notebook · pdf</text>
        </g>

        <!-- arrows (animated stroke) -->
        <g stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)" stroke-width="1" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arr)">
          <path class="anim-path" d="M100,44 L130,44" pathLength="100" stroke-dasharray="100" stroke-dashoffset="100" style="animation:draw 1.2s ease forwards .3s"></path>
          <path class="anim-path" d="M216,44 L246,44" pathLength="100" stroke-dasharray="100" stroke-dashoffset="100" style="animation:draw 1.2s ease forwards .6s"></path>
          <path class="anim-path" d="M289,68 C 289,90 220,90 173,110" pathLength="100" stroke-dasharray="100" stroke-dashoffset="100" style="animation:draw 1.4s ease forwards .9s"></path>
          <path class="anim-path" d="M130,134 L100,134" pathLength="100" stroke-dasharray="100" stroke-dashoffset="100" style="animation:draw 1.2s ease forwards 1.2s"></path>
          <path class="anim-path" d="M216,134 L246,134" pathLength="100" stroke-dasharray="100" stroke-dashoffset="100" style="animation:draw 1.2s ease forwards 1.5s"></path>
          <path class="anim-path" d="M173,158 C 173,180 173,180 173,200" pathLength="100" stroke-dasharray="100" stroke-dashoffset="100" style="animation:draw 1.2s ease forwards 1.8s"></path>
        </g>

        <!-- small chart bottom-right -->
        <g transform="translate(330,210)">
          <line x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="-44" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" stroke-width="1"></line>
          <line x1="0" y1="0" x2="84" y2="0" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" stroke-width="1"></line>
          <polyline points="2,-12 16,-22 30,-18 44,-30 58,-26 72,-36 82,-32"
            fill="none" stroke="#5e6ad2" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
            pathLength="100" stroke-dasharray="100" stroke-dashoffset="100" style="animation:draw 1.6s ease forwards 2s"></polyline>
          <circle cx="82" cy="-32" r="2.5" fill="#ba9cff" opacity="0">
            <animate attributeName="opacity" from="0" to="1" begin="3.4s" dur=".4s" fill="freeze"></animate>
          </circle>
        </g>
        <text x="330" y="244" font-family="JetBrains Mono" font-size="9" fill="#6a6b6c">val_loss</text>
      </svg>

      <div class="hero-caption mono">
        <span>fig.1 — analysis pipeline (draft)</span>
        <span>↻ continuous iteration</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
